Title: Puppy Love
Writer: Greg Glienna, Peter Stass, Kirsten Guenther
Actors: Lucy Hale, Grant Gustin, Nore Davis
Plot: After a disastrous first date, Nicole and Max vow to lose each other's numbers until their dogs find a love match. Hilariously mismatched Nicole and Max are forced to become responsible co-parents, but end up finding love themselves.
